Store name: Nike Run Shop

Product: Running shoes (Mens, Womens, Boys and Girls).

15 shoes per category

Image Specs (from original images):
  - Dimensions: 592 x 592
  - Size: ~ 20kb
  - Images stored in db and accessed via django template



